Package gr.aueb.cf.ch11_ch12.exercises_ch12.bankapp.model

This package includes the following model classes:
Holder
JointAccount
OverdraftAccount
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Holder
    Defines an account's holder Credentials.
    Includes Holder.id, Holder.firstname, Holder.lastname, Holder.ssn
    With accessor methods: Holder.getId(), Holder.getFirstname(), Holder.getLastname(), Holder.getSsn()
    Public API methods:
    Holder.convertToString()
    Validation method:
    Holder.isSsnValid(String)
    JointAccount
    Defines a joint account's Credentials.
    Includes JointAccount.id, JointAccount.jointAccHolder1, JointAccount.jointAccHolder2, JointAccount.iban, JointAccount.balance
    With mutator methods: JointAccount.setBalance(double)
    And accessor methods: JointAccount.getId(), JointAccount.getJointAccHolder1(), JointAccount.getJointAccHolder2(), JointAccount.getIban(), JointAccount.getBalance()
    Public API methods:
    JointAccount.deposit(double), JointAccount.withdraw(double, Holder), JointAccount.getJointAccBalance(), JointAccount.getJointAccountState()
    Validation method:
    JointAccount.isValidHolder(Holder)
    OverdraftAccount
    Defines an OverdraftAccount OverdraftAccount.
    Includes id, overdraftHolder, iban, balance
    With mutator methods: setBalance(double)
    And accessor methods: getId(), getOverdraftHolder(), getIban(), getBalance()
    Public API methods:
    deposit(double), withdraw(double, Holder), getOverdraftAccBalance(), getOverdraftAccState()
    Validation method:
    isValidOverdraftHolder(Holder)
